  "id": "RAW_55817313",
  "title": "“工程师”正式上岗：万卷智能携手浙江交工，发布可独立工作的 Engineer Agent",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NDkyMTQ5Mw==&mid=2247499590&idx=1&sn=44851e376859462842bbf8e014fa2bf5",
  "date": "2026-03-06 05:27:00",
  "author": " 有新Newin",
  "siteName": "有新Newin",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015933\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4212962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"237\" data-imgfileid=\"100015935\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=00851b4c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPQ3MNFbl39eIwHzicLA4ic9sndXD6dhln8yR1d7rNoibialmuLXtzhOMia1gwY2WBCHO8U51pILmkh2w4U0GmvwZtFyQpuUlFJgdTfzSNZicwktyw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"173\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100012589\" data-ratio=\"0.3074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=05f1e27c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHfpLmI5MibCVKPa7bw396N24gBz2qTSicrwzRYAvvwsU9Agh6QzwKffAxiaf0f67iaicXic0gu39TFeIEsA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015464\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-aiimagesource=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"有新Newin\" data-alias=\"NewinData\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/wqO5B9doEHfWpviblkX0cCTHkGRJYxSBgwSqgeKicI9Qm9jOia9oQ19BsiblkJBYDAsu0moqoJrZ8xCC5oWyDjoViaQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"探索新科技，聚焦新价值。\" data-id=\"Mzg3NDkyMTQ5Mw==\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"2\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在 AI 浪潮席卷数字世界的今天，一个更现实的问题开始被频繁提起：AI 什么时候才能真正进入工业现场，而不是停留在代码、文档和聊天窗口里？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">2026 年 3 月 5 日，万卷智能（Colleague+）与行业龙头浙江交工集团在杭州给出了一次明确回应。这不仅是一场产品公测发布，更是一种新的工作关系的出现—— AI 不再只是辅助工具，而开始</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\">以“工程师同事”的身份参与真实生产流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015936\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"384\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100015939\" data-ratio=\"0.6833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=748dd3f8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FPQ3MNFbl39evrGGqnCw2tu8nu2AxVib1eZDX0zbtaEpvoOicIl7j84uBeFtewDcPdchhickibOewrxcmNaHQsJVPvFhs02EOkUSzKhicNg3Lm05w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015931\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;\">发布会现场创始团队合照</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015931\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">发布会现场，万卷智能 CEO 李天翔给出了一句核心判断：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">“让 AI 成为物理世界的专业工程师。”</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;在他的理解里，工程行业并不缺工具，真正缺的是能够承担完整工作链条的“数字劳动力”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">范式变化：Agent 正在缩短工程师的工作边界</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">如果回看过去三十年工程行业的数字化进程，会发现它几乎是一部典型的“工具进化史”。从最早的手绘图纸，到 CAD，再到三维 BIM，软件不断升级，但角色始终没有发生根本变化——它们只是工程师手中的“画笔”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在这种模式下，软件提升的是效率，而不是生产结构。工程师依然需要逐页阅读图纸与规范，手动完成分析、判断与报告撰写。工具再强，工作主体仍然是人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">万卷智能试图改变这一底层逻辑。公司提出&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">Engineer Agent（工程师智能体）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;的新范式，其核心是直接提供能够承担工程任务的“数字劳动力”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">万卷智能 CEO 李天翔在发布会上提出一个关键判断：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">“在 AI-Native 时代，人类工程师的工作边界会明显收窄，未来 Engineer Agent 可以独立承担 30%～50% 的专业工作。”</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这意味着工程师与 AI 的关系正在发生变化。过去的软件只是辅助工具，而在新的结构中，Agent 更像是一位能够独立完成任务的同事。工程师负责关键判断与最终决策，Agent 则承担大量系统化、重复性和资料密集型工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">从行业规模来看，这一变化背后对应的是一个巨大的工程服务市场。全球工程服务市场在 2024 年规模约&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">3.4 万亿美元</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">，预计到 2030 年将增长至&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">4.7 万亿美元</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。其中大量工作集中在设计、评估与技术咨询等知识密集型环节，而这些正是 AI Agent 最有可能改变的部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">李天翔认为，工程行业之所以适合被 Agent 重构，是因为其工作逻辑高度结构化。无论是交通基建、能源工程还是高端制造，大多数工程任务都遵循类似流程：阅读图纸与规范、理解技术资料、进行系统分析、最终输出设计或评估成果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">当这条逻辑链条被结构化之后，工程工作就可以被拆解为可执行任务，由 Engineer Agent 完成其中的大部分环节。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在 Colleague+ 的工作模式中，工程师只需要提出需求并上传项目资料，系统便会自动完成图纸与技术文件解析、逻辑推理与成果生成。例如在高速公路安全评估场景中，一份涉及上万页资料的工程报告，Agent 可以在&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">2～3 小时</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;内完成分析并输出成果，而传统模式下，一名资深工程师往往需要&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">约 2 周时间</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;才能完成同样任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这种变化带来的不仅是效率提升，更是工程工作结构的改变。过去的模式是“人力 + 工具”，工程师需要亲自完成资料阅读、分析与报告编写；而在新的模式中，逐渐变成“人类工程师 + AI 同事”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">实战案例：全球首个施工安全 Agent</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">如果说 AI Agent 的愿景代表着未来工程生产方式的变化，那么真正决定技术价值的，仍然是具体工程场景里的落地能力，万卷智能在发布会上展示的核心案例来自与浙江交工集团的联合实践。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">浙江交工是浙江交通投资集团旗下核心施工企业，业务覆盖道路、桥梁、隧道、市政、港航等交通基础设施建设领域，在建项目遍布全国 31 个省份，并延伸至全球 21 个国家。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">对于这样一家长期承担大型工程建设任务的企业而言，复杂项目所带来的安全评估与风险管理需求，本身就是一个高度专业化的工作场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">浙江交工在发布会上也总结了当前行业面临的三大痛点：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">行业整体进入转型阶段，企业需要在传统施工之外探索新的增长曲线；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">工程项目复杂度不断提高，跨海桥梁、地下工程等项目系统性更强；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">业务规模扩大与高水平技术人才之间的结构性矛盾逐渐显现。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在实际工程中，一份完整的施工安全风险评估报告往往涉及大量资料。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">施工图纸、地质勘察报告、施工组织设计文件以及大量规范条文，需要工程师逐项阅读与比对；此外，很多大型项目的技术文档规模动辄上万页，一名资深工程师往往需要耗费数周时间才能完成分析并形成完整报告。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"383\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100015920\" data-ratio=\"0.6805555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7093ea5a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FPQ3MNFbl39eLibiaHYlag01SsQKCU0w4N8iaasLxZpE0ZlTBib9gyiaibib3Baw9WkTwVicPsFz7VCklF7g0ZOy6dPiceicQ9zZ17fkXZ7cHGFunpv70Y%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015931\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;\">交通建设工程 AI Agent 联合实验室揭牌仪式现场</span></span></p>\n  <p data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6809309309309309\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"3996\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015918\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"1\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在这样的背景下，浙江交工与万卷智能启动联合研发合作，并成立交通建设工程 AI Agent 联合实验室，尝试将 AI 技术引入工程安全风险评估环节，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">双方合作的目标，是打造行业首个“施工安全风险评估 Agent”，其背后包含了三大逻辑：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">多模态深度解析：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;它自动读取了数万页 PDF 图纸、复杂的地质勘察报告与施工组织设计，不仅能识别文字，更能理解图纸中的结构标注。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">跨文档关联推理：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">智能体自动识别设计图纸和施工组织报告中的细微数据冲突，完成自动更正，并高亮提示给工程师。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">规范对齐与交付：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;它自动引用最新版《公路桥涵设计规范》条文进行校核，生成风险评估段落。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">传统模式下，一名资深工程师通常需要约两周时间，甚至由专家团队连续数周协作，才能完成一份涉及上千页资料的复杂工程安全评估报告。而在智能体参与后，系统可以在数小时内完成资料解析、逻辑推理与报告生成，准确率达到&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">98% 以上</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">，整体评估效率相比传统模式提升&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">50 倍以上</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在完整流程中，Agent 可以完成从&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">设计桩长与承台高度识别 → 风险系数计算 → 风险等级判定</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;的闭环推理过程，这种系统化分析能力，也让工程安全评估开始从“人工逐页阅读资料”的人力密集型模式，转向“智能体自动解析工程文档”的技术驱动模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">产品“金三角”：构筑物理与数字的闭环</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">如果说 Agent 的应用落地只是第一步，那么真正决定这类技术能否长期进入工程行业核心生产流程的，是背后的技术架构。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"316\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100015921\" data-ratio=\"0.562037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74663456&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FPQ3MNFbl39djibkfjHFqibjWChbxXSiajOZF4xNJR9KFneSvibw9TFLRYBy5ZRETXO7sLHDrceMtemK5TSa5ibOTzaMJ5fMG9vibR4jZ3SICzrgIA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015931\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;\">万卷智能产品“金三角”技术图解</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">万卷智能在发布会上展示的，是一套围绕工程现场构建的 AI-Native 系统结构——由&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">Pocket Engineer 硬件终端、Colleague+ 平台以及 Engineer Agents 智能体集群</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">构成的产品“金三角”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">1）Pocket Engineer（智能硬件）—— 物理世界的入口</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">一款面向工程现场设计的便携式智能终端设备，被称为“口袋工程师”。工程人员在桥梁、隧道或路基施工现场，可以通过拍照、视频记录或语音交互，将现场信息实时输入系统。与传统手机采集不同，这类设备会同步记录空间坐标、时间信息以及多模态数据，并自动进入 Colleague+ 平台的工程数据库，从而形成连续的现场数据流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这意味着，Agent 不仅能阅读图纸，还能同时理解现场。系统可以自动识别构件尺寸、空间位置关系，判断桥梁支座与设计图纸是否一致，识别施工安全隐患，例如临边防护缺失或违规操作等问题，实现从“读文档”到“看现场”的能力升级。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">2）Colleague+ Platform（智能原生平台）—— 能力底座</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这一平台构成了整个系统的知识中枢和调度中心。平台内部存储大量行业规范、历史工程案例、施工流程以及专家经验，并通过多模态解析能力处理不同类型的工程数据，包括文本规范、CAD 图纸、BIM 模型以及现场影像。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在系统运行过程中，Colleague+ 不只是一个数据存储平台，更像是一位始终在线的“数字总工”。它可以自动检索工程规范、进行多步逻辑推理，并协调不同智能体之间的任务分工，使得复杂工程问题能够被拆解为一系列可执行任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">3）Engineer Agents（智能体群）—— 执行核心</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">与通用 AI 模型不同，这些智能体是围绕具体工程场景训练的专家型 Agent。例如有的智能体负责图纸解析，有的负责工程量计算，有的负责规范校核，还有的负责风险评估。它们在平台调度下协同工作，最终形成完整的工程分析结果或报告。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"375\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100015930\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=09544e16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FPQ3MNFbl39eBFOhVoUMamyEOzXEpVibcXPj1bSQAY6KSMxaBlnkZic9JyQ7akmzqn19aX3W9S1ZMAjQ934quYwUNr4g5DB8JbKuGU75u9Crfg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;\">创始人&amp;CEO 李天翔（右）现场演示</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这套体系构成了一个完整的 “感知 — 认知 — 执行”闭环。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在这种结构下，AI 不仅存在于云端的软件工具，还会逐渐进入真实工程环境之中。从读取图纸、理解规范，到识别现场情况，再到生成分析报告，系统能够覆盖工程项目多个关键环节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">万卷智能所展示的是一套面向工程行业构建的 AI 基础设施。通过软硬一体的架构，Agent 才真正具备了进入工程现场、参与实际决策的可能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">跨界迁移，从交通基建到</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">高端制造</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">万卷智能选择从交通基础设施工程切入，并不是偶然。在整个工程行业中，高速公路、桥梁与隧道等交通工程往往被认为是最复杂的一类场景。这些项目涉及大量专业规范、复杂结构设计以及高度非标准化的数据体系，工程资料规模巨大，决策逻辑也高度依赖专家经验，因此长期以来被视为 AI 最难进入的行业之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">正因如此，万卷智能将这一领域视为工程 AI 的“技术高地”。如果智能体能够在交通基建这一复杂场景中完成图纸解析、工程推理与风险评估，那么其底层能力也将具备天然的跨行业迁移潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">万卷智能的商业逻辑是：掌握了“最难”的逻辑，便能赋能“更多”的场景。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;这种基于“通用专业逻辑引擎”的能力，正在向其他高端制造赛道自然溢出：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"color:#0080ff;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">新能源汽车：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">辅助工程师进行成千上万个零部件的设计校核与DFM（可制造性设计）审核，大幅缩短车型迭代周期。</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"color:#0080ff;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">商业航天（如金属3D打印）：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">在极高精度的设计约束下，Agent能自动完成结构仿真分析与安全性校验，降低试错成本。</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">对于新能源汽车和航天等行业来说，这意味着企业不需要为每一个场景重新开发 AI 系统，而可以直接使用一套已经具备工程推理能力的智能体平台。换句话说，万卷智能提供的是一种可复用的工程智能基础设施，这种跨行业的能力迁移，也让 Engineer Agent 的商业边界远不止交通工程本身。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">万卷智能，一家正在定义未来生产力的公司</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">“读万卷书，育智能体”，是万卷智能对自身路径的一种概括。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">从浙江大学计算机技术创新研究院孵化，到获得高通创投、红杉中国等顶级机构的认可，万卷智能在短短几年间完成了从技术探索到产业落地的关键跨越。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">通过与浙江交工成立“交通建设工程AI Agent联合实验室”，万卷不仅是在做产品，更是在深度参与行业标准的制定；在这个过程中，万卷智能逐渐构建起以工程数据与专家思维为核心的技术飞轮。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">一方面，通过多模态解析能力持续读取工程图纸、技术规范与项目资料，在万页级上下文中形成系统理解；另一方面，在真实项目中不断积累工程数据与专家经验，让智能体逐步学习工程师的分析路径与决策逻辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">“我们的愿景是让 AI 成为全球工程师的同事。”万卷智能 CEO 李天翔博士表示。在这一构想中，AI 将是具备岗位能力的执行智能体，能够阅读工程资料、理解复杂逻辑，并输出可用于工程验收的专业成果，从而承担一部分原本由工程师完成的专业工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">万卷智能并未宣称技术已经完全成熟，而是通过一次次真实项目实践持续打磨系统能力，从每一份 PDF 图纸的解析到每一份风险评估报告的生成，一步步接近由 AI 与工程师协同工作的未来；随着 Pre-A 轮融资的开启，万卷智能也正在寻找更多志同道合的投资人与产业伙伴，共同参与这场工程行业的技术变革。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">万卷智能（Colleague+）将自己定义为一家全球领先的工程师智能体（Engineer Agent）提供商，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">致力于让 AI 成为工程师的同事，以交通基建为技术高地，向商业航天、新能源汽车等领域输出可跨域迁移的 Agent 能力，推动工程生产方式的智能化升级，释放全球专家级劳动力。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "万卷智能联合浙江交工发布 Engineer Agent，通过软硬一体架构实现工程安全评估效率提升 50 倍，标志着 AI 从辅助工具向独立“数字劳动力”转变。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "万卷智能联合浙江交工发布 Engineer Agent，通过软硬一体架构实现工程安全评估效率提升 50 倍，标志着 AI 从辅助工具向独立“数字劳动力”转变。",
  "summary": "文章详细报道了万卷智能（Colleague+）发布的工程师智能体（Engineer Agent）及其在交通基建领域的落地实践。核心产品体系由 Pocket Engineer 硬件终端、Colleague+ 平台及智能体集群构成的“金三角”架构组成，实现了从物理现场感知到云端逻辑推理的闭环。通过与浙江交工的联合研发，该系统在施工安全风险评估场景中，将原本需要资深工程师耗时 2 周的工作缩短至 2-3 小时，准确率达 98%。文章强调，AI 正在从单纯的效率工具演变为能够承担完整工作链条的“数字同事”，并展示了该技术向新能源汽车、商业航天等高端制造领域跨界迁移的潜力。",
